ant:ant:1.6/post-gen/pi-post-gen-2026-04-28T01-38-57-693351Z.log`.\n\nNext steps:\n1. Review the preserved branch and keep only the native-safe, library-specific tests; the post-gen report already identifies 5 generated tests that failed for non-metadata reasons.\n2. Investigate the `RegexpMatcherFactory` / `Jdk14RegexpMatcher` reflective loading path and adjust metadata or test-side native-image config so the default matcher is retained and instantiable in native image.\n3. Re-run `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=ant:ant:1.6` and `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=ant:ant:1.6` (plus the future-defaults lane if needed)."}}
